  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-002",
    "scene_index": 2,
    "text": "而是孩子每天都在上课、每天都在写作业，",
    "start_time": 3.35,
    "end_time": 6.46,
    "image_asset_id": "e859496b-6c68-490a-9621-772e142895b1",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-e85949\\local_1783652608434_e859496b.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-003",
    "scene_index": 3,
    "text": "看起来特别忙，最后一检查，原来的问题一个都没解决。",
    "start_time": 6.46,
    "end_time": 11.166,
    "image_asset_id": "8618306a-d15e-418d-8f71-b791bb2ba9de",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-861830\\local_1783652605763_8618306a.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-004",
    "scene_index": 4,
    "text": "为什么？",
    "start_time": 11.166,
    "end_time": 12.044,
    "image_asset_id": "2d9e3976-4ff2-4885-8da2-19c442cb7f1f",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-2d9e39\\local_1783652602230_2d9e3976.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-005",
    "scene_index": 5,
    "text": "因为很多孩子暑假学习，做的是统一的内容。",
    "start_time": 12.044,
    "end_time": 15.712,
    "image_asset_id": "d38efa5f-b64b-4c76-82a8-5d14271c67cc",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-d38efa\\local_1783652599383_d38efa5f.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-006",
    "scene_index": 6,
    "text": "基础好的觉得太简单，基础弱的又跟不上。",
    "start_time": 15.712,
    "end_time": 19.222,
    "image_asset_id": "168d0ada-c7bd-424c-bb16-cf8078728591",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-168d0a\\local_1783652596141_168d0ada.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-007",
    "scene_index": 7,
    "text": "老师讲了很多，孩子也记了很多笔记，但是没人先弄清楚：",
    "start_time": 19.222,
    "end_time": 24.087,
    "image_asset_id": "d6622279-6cc1-4f4d-aaf9-cefbe43c472c",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-d66222\\local_1783652593843_d6622279.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-008",
    "scene_index": 8,
    "text": "他到底是知识不会，方法不对，计算容易错，还是根本没有形成学习习惯？",
    "start_time": 24.087,
    "end_time": 30.308,
    "image_asset_id": "a9fdc753-f7e9-430f-88fa-a0d542d9f506",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-a9fdc7\\local_1783652590935_a9fdc753.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-009",
    "scene_index": 9,
    "text": "暑期时间很短，最忌讳的就是所有孩子用同一套办法。",
    "start_time": 30.308,
    "end_time": 34.615,
    "image_asset_id": "7702774c-ce14-4f66-bf6e-105738af08b3",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-770277\\local_1783652587976_7702774c.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-010",
    "scene_index": 10,
    "text": "真正有效的第一步，不是马上开始补课，而是先找到孩子目前最影响成绩的几个问题。",
    "start_time": 34.615,
    "end_time": 41.395,
    "image_asset_id": "65c61f2a-a79f-4c63-b63c-d7ba5cb4b46e",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-65c61f\\local_1783652585202_65c61f2a.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-011",
    "scene_index": 11,
    "text": "我们给孩子上体验课之前，会先通过试卷、错题和现场练习，",
    "start_time": 41.395,
    "end_time": 46.021,
    "image_asset_id": "7d49aebb-54be-4699-9226-a92056f43265",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-7d49ae\\local_1783652582218_7d49aebb.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-012",
    "scene_index": 12,
    "text": "看清楚孩子问题到底在哪里。",
    "start_time": 46.021,
    "end_time": 48.334,
    "image_asset_id": "b2bf3da6-7c96-4de9-b2f8-a1df3c29ff23",
    "image_path": "C:\\Users\\Admin\\Desktop\\短视频\\douyin-video-tool-source-code\\douyin-mcp-local\\image-assets\\generated\\20260710-图片生成-Generate one stand-b2bf3d\\local_1783652579799_b2bf3da6.png"
  },
  {
    "segment_id": "seg-013",
    "scene_index": 13,
    "text": "仪征的家长，可以带孩子来做一次学习情况分析。",
    "start_time": 48.334,
    "end_time": 52.322,
    "image_asset_id": "6337a7a6-4162-4c95-a8f6-96965b6023d6",
